data.description: Welcome to the prestigious Windstone Village Golf Course Community, where elegance meets tranquility. Nestled amidst the rolling hills of Ringgold, Georgia, 83 Hummingbird Hill is located in a beautiful gated community and stands as a testament to luxurious living in this sought-after neighborhood. This splendid 5-bedroom, 3.5-bathroom residence exudes timeless elegance, from the stately brick facade to the meticulous landscaping that surrounds it. The classic design and meticulous attention to detail make it a standout in Windstone Village. The spacious layout promotes a sense of togetherness, with the two separate living rooms, dining, and kitchen areas flowing seamlessly. Natural light streams through large windows, accentuating the warm tones of the interior. The kitchen is a chef's delight, featuring sleek countertops, modern appliances, and ample storage. The master bedroom is a true sanctuary, offering a peaceful haven to unwind. With an attached well-appointed bathroom, it's a private oasis within the home.Additional bedrooms can effortlessly adapt to your needs, whether you envision a guest room, home office, or hobby space.Walk downstairs to the completely finished basement and enjoy this totally separate living  area complete with a kitchen and so much more. The property boasts an expansive deck, perfect for entertaining, stargazing, or simply relishing the tranquility of the area. Imagine summer barbecues, morning coffee, and evening sunsets in this idyllic setting.If you've been dreaming of a life that combines elegance, comfort, and community, your dream has found a home at 83 Hummingbird Hill in Windstone Village. This is your chance to experience the epitome of upscale living. Call today!*This property is being sold in it's ''as in condition''*
